Titolo: Faith: The Unholy Trinity

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Faith, also known as Faith: The Unholy Trinity, is a survival horror video game, created and published by Airdorf Games and published by New Blood Interactive. The game is planned to span three chapters, the first of which was published in 2017 on Steam and itch.io for the PC.
The game uses retro graphics similar to the graphics of an Apple II or Atari 2600.

